Paper: hep-th/9412156

Date: 1994-12-18

Title: Quantal Overlapping Resonance Criterion in the Pullen Edmonds Model

Authors: S. Graffi, V.R. Manfredi, L. Salasnich

Comments: 12 pages, LATEX, 2 figures available upon request to the Authors,

submitted to Mod. Phys. Lett. BJournal-ref: Mod. Phys. Lett. B7 (1995) 747-753

In order to highlight the onset of chaos in the Pullen-Edmonds model aquantal analog of the resonance overlap criterion has been examined. A quitegood agreement between analytical and numerical results is obtained.